  <brief_title>Symptom Control and Impact on Daily Life in Patients With Gastroesophageal Reflux Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Observational Study to Describe Symptom Control and Impact on Daily Life in Patients With Gastroesophageal Reflux Disease (GERD)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
